               <p>SECOND DAY. FRIDAY, JANUARY 12, 1827.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury - before Mr. Recorder.</p>
               <p>294. 
               
                  <persName id="t18270111-16-defend228" type="defendantName">
                     CHARLES 
                     PEARCE
                  <interp inst="t18270111-16-defend228" type="surname" value="PEARCE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270111-16-defend228" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>
