             were indicted for <rs id="t18270111-16-off94" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18270111-16-off94" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270111-16-off94" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18270111-16-cd95" type="crimeDate">20th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270111-16-off94 t18270111-16-cd95"></join>, at <placeName id="t18270111-16-crimeloc96">St. Mary-le-bone</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t18270111-16-crimeloc96" type="placeName" value="St. Mary-le-bone"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270111-16-crimeloc96" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270111-16-off94 t18270111-16-crimeloc96"></join>, 2 reticules, value 15s.; 1 bottle, value 5s.; 8 pairs of shoes, value 30s.; 18 glass candle ornaments, value 20s.; 24 pairs of gloves, value 30s., and 1 trunk, value 4s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18270111-16-victim232" type="victimName">
                           Henry 
                           Sansom
                        <interp inst="t18270111-16-victim232" type="surname" value="Sansom"></interp>
